title: Pixel 5 won't connect to 5G in Australia
content: I have a brand new Pixel5 purchased locally in Australia. The phone has been set up but will not connect to Telstra 5G network. I took the phone into a Telstra shop yesterday who supplied a new SIM card and advised it would be operational on 5G after an hour or so , however it it still not connecting to Telstra 5G. The area's I am in are prime metro signal area's but the phone is operating on 4G only. I have the January update,
